OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,FVicki Crawford's fight for justice
OL,7,Fagainst her childhood abuser "broke"
OL,8,Fher, leaving her with a number of
OL,9,Fmental health issues and wanting to
OL,10,Fwithdraw from the whole court process.
OL,12,FDelays in the Crown Court have reached
OL,13,Frecord levels in England and Wales
OL,14,Fwith 73,105 outstanding cases as of
OL,15,FSeptember 2024 and it is having a
OL,16,Fmajor impact on victims like Ms
OL,17,FCrawford.
