OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,FShe was groomed and sexually abused by
OL,7,Fan older man when she was 14 but
OL,8,Fdidn't report the crime to police
OL,9,Funtil 2018, more than 30 years later.
OL,11,F"I didn't really realise what it was
OL,12,Funtil I was 29, when my friend pointed
OL,13,Fout that it wasn't a relationship,
OL,14,Fthat it was childhood sexual abuse,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
OL,17,FHer abuser was charged in 2021.
