OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,FBut it took five years and eight
OL,7,Fmonths for her case to get to trial
OL,8,Fdue to a number of different delays
OL,9,Fwithin the court system.
OL,11,F"What made it difficult was being
OL,12,Fbounced around with various court
OL,13,Fdates, so you'd get to the day that
OL,14,Fwas supposed to be the trial and you'd
OL,15,Fget told at 3 or 4 in the afternoon
OL,16,Fthat the trial wasn't going to go
OL,17,Fahead," she said.
