OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,F"So you'd sit in limbo for that month
OL,7,Fand then the trial date would come
OL,8,Fonly for the same thing to happen
OL,9,Fagain.
OL,11,F"I ended up with agoraphobia, PTSD, I
OL,12,Fcouldn't sleep at night, I'd have
OL,13,Fnightmares, I'd wake up in the middle
OL,14,Fof panic attacks, I'd have migraine
OL,15,Fafter migraine in the run up to court
OL,16,Fdates.
OL,18,F"Each time it got worse, each time I
OL,19,Ffelt increasingly anxious."
