OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,FShe said the fifth delay "broke" her
OL,7,Fand she just wanted to withdraw from
OL,8,Fthe whole process.
OL,10,F"The system itself, the lack of
OL,11,Ffunding, just makes it impossible to
OL,12,Fnavigate as a complainant," Ms
OL,13,FCrawford said.
OL,15,FHer experience with the criminal
OL,16,Fjustice system is far from unique.
OL,18,FThe backlog in the Crown Court has
OL,19,Falmost doubled in five years with
OL,20,Fnearly 50% of victims having their
OL,21,Ftrial adjourned at least once.
