OL,3,C'I couldn't sleep': Victims wait years
OL,4,Cfor justice amid record court backlog
OL,6,F"That has to have an impact because
OL,7,Fyou can't move forward.
OL,9,F"It saddens me, and sickens me,
OL,10,Fenrages me."
OL,12,FIn her report released on Tuesday into
OL,13,Fthe extent of the crown court backlog,
OL,14,FBaroness Newlove has made a number of
OL,15,Frecommendations, including better
OL,16,Fcommunication with victims, creating a
OL,17,Fsingle point of contact for victims of
OL,18,Fcrime, restoring court inspectors and
OL,19,Fincreasing financial support for
OL,20,Fvictims.
