OL,6,F"The expenses they can claim back is
OL,7,Fbelow minimum wage; it is absolutely
OL,8,Fdisgraceful what they're given,"
OL,9,FBaroness Newlove said.
OL,11,FShe said it was crucial victims still
OL,12,Ffelt encouraged to come forward and
OL,13,Fseek justice.
